summary: honestly now when i hear people saying they want Jon Snow to be king I'm like, "why do you hate him? why do you want him to...
question: honestly now when i hear people saying they want Jon Snow to be king I'm like, "why do you hate him? why do you want him to suffer?" because lemme tell you something, that non-kingdom-wanting boy has about a year of standing tall before he melts down over a council meeting for grain rationing. "I CANT DO IT ANYMOH MAH LORDS!"
answer: lmao yeah… jon doesn’t want the crown, which is exactly why he would be a good king. however, i don’t think he could handle it. being lord commander, king in the north, he really loathes responsibility which i get because he has so many people that depend on him. he’s not politically educated or versed so that’s a big problem too. just let jon snow rest lol, when was the last time the poor man had a good nap?

Summary:

Sansa Stark’s mother is keen on her two older children marrying. They go into King’s Landing as guests of King Rhaegar’s good faith in his estranged family to his son, Jon/Aegon Targaryen. The thing is, it seems as though Prince Jon Targaryen looks down on people who do not have wealth and mainly, are from the North. But she doesn’t care about Jon when she meets the charming and handsome Joffrey. With his light air about him and how he is not a brooding jerk like Jon, Sansa may think marriage isn’t so bad. Except Jon and Joffrey know and hate each other. Secrets unravel and Sansa has to check within herself before she may make the biggest mistake of her life.

summary: Why do you think Jon completely ignored Dany in episode 2? He wouldn't even look at her.  I love reading your thoughts and was...
body:
Why do you think Jon completely ignored Dany in episode 2? He wouldn’t even look at her.  I love reading your thoughts and was hoping you could shed some light on this☺

@rihbreezyfan 

Hi!

He’s delaying the inevitable imho. Jon was dumped a piece of information that he can’t, in good conscience, keep from Dany, but he doesn’t want to tell her either, so his knee-jerk reaction is to avoid her like the plague. Even just looking at her directly without spilling the beans would probably make him feel like he’s deceiving her.

I’m glad you like my blog! I know I haven’t been all that active recently XD

blog.name: waking-dreams-of-harmony
blog.title: Headcanon is the new reality...
blog.description:
Hi there! My name is Ellie! Welcome to my tumblr!  Just thought I'd add a few things to know about me and my blog! If my url gives you any clues, at the heart of this tumblr, I'm a proud Harmony shipper through and through. And while I do still reblog HHR and Dan and Emma content (and I always will) you will find that the majority of my focus has shifted to Jonerys (Jon x Daenerys from Game of Thrones). And while you might have to do a little deep blogging to find my reblogs on these, I also ship--both passionately and casually--Cesare x Lucrezia, Mulder x Scully, Lizzington for a while until tptb started to mess with it, Baker x Lawson (Bawson), all the Sense8 ships though Kalagang is my #1, Clint x Natasha (Clintasha), Jane x Thor (Fosterson), Darcy x Loki (Tasertricks), Darcy x Steve (Shieldshock), Kili x Tauriel (Kiliel), Superman x Wonder Woman (Superwonder), and more than I have space for or the memory to list. 
I do my best to tag every post so that if something is your notp, it's nsfw, or it's triggering, you can blacklist it. That said, if you follow me and there is something that you need tagged in order to make it a happy place for you to explore, come into my inbox and let me know :) You will also see a lot of politically charged reblogs in support of women, the queer/gender-queer and trans community, BLM, Muslims, POC, Jewish people, the mentally ill, and austistic people. I'm strongly pro choice, pro inter-sectional feminism, and refuse to call the angry cheeto currently living in the white house president. If anything like that offends you, this might not be the right blog for you.
Last little few things to throw out there: I'm 35, I plan to adopt at least 4 cats (or more) at some point and be that cat lady everyone's always whispering about, and I tend to greet and converse with everyone I meet like an overeager puppy. 
Whew! Sorry for the long intro folks! Please enjoy your time here, and remember, you're always welcome to come in and say hi!
